andom, as are playing chess, solitaire, drinking, etc.  Not much self control there people, plus they never get along, and I find the relationships to be rather cryptic - plus the ""rumour"" system could be useful to some degree - but I find it clunky.I recommend this for what it is, just make sure you know what this game is before you buy it - and try to get in on sale for crying out loud.  Steam ALWAYS has sales.  Heck, it's 50% off right meow.p.s. I wish I could combine several parts of this game in a blender with DayZ, 7 Days to Die, Rust, Rebuild 1 and 2 (if you haven't tried these, check out Sarah Northway's brainchildren.. and Rebuild 3 on the way), Dead State and State of Decay and have the perfect zombocalypse (I know, not a word - but I like it) game pop out."
