76561197978374804,Recommended,249360,788348,"Posted: 8 September, 2013",all,Faded Tiger,"An interesting difficult game. There are 3 diffrent modes which drasticly effect the difficulty of the game (and they are shown as difficulties). The games general idea is that you either are trying to survive as long as possible, or to get out of the town, via rebuilding a vehicle or waiting/finding out where rescue will come. Each person is given diffrent commands, such as gathering, boarding up a house, watching for zombies, improving equipment. Moving from house to house is dangerous, as it is extreemly risky, you have to fight against the clock, but rushing will get you killed, fast. It is an extreemly tactical game though it can at times be a bit repetative, in the same was as a roguelike can be. Every play through is diffrent, and there is a lot of customization options to put in your own pictures for places and survivors, as well as making custom survivor stats, which can completly change thegame (making it impossible or a walkthrough). Overall if you like tactical games, and don't mind a HELL of a challenge, it's very fun. The only thing I might add is that you have to manage the relationship between your survivors and it can be very very frustrating."
